{"tid":1682381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尹兆堅就屯門不明氣體洩露提緊急質詢 梁君彥指不符急切條件拒絕","createTime":"2019-10-30T04:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T05:44:58.000Z","uid":1886,"like":8,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4984ba3bc12e2bca24b54eecc71b87ebd0f9a43a","tid":1682381,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:20:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsdb.memehk.com/img/post/20939_301019A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsdb.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F20939_301019A.jpg&h=4186478c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員尹兆堅要求於立法會會議提出急切質詢，要求保安局交代前日下午在屯門出現類似催淚彈氣味事件，立法會主席梁君彥拒絕要求。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥書面回覆尹兆堅指，有關質詢不符合性質急切的條件，尹兆堅應考慮於其他渠道跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488967-20191030.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488967-20191030.htm&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt3yIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=fdbba3af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488967-20191030.htm&h=9b01f5fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488967-20191030.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a3a38f7686358dc49977a9fbf5e293489ceb3c7e","tid":1682381,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"368a63bdba52221f28df56f9f7e2c542256f9125","tid":1682381,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T04:21:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">已經有13個英美參議員/單位就GPhone出聲<br />\n快啲Rt and like and reply哂佢<br />\n全部響哂 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">/Task1</span></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s